innotop (1.15.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version 1.15.3
  * Modernize debian packaging:
    - Bump debhelper-compat to 13 (drop debian/compat)
    - Bump Standards-Version to 4.7.2
    - Fix Architecture from any to all (pure Perl package)
    - Add Vcs-Git and Vcs-Browser fields
    - Add Rules-Requires-Root: no
    - Add debian/watch for uscan
    - Remove debian/files build artifact
    - Fix and complete copyright information
    - Lowercase first word of Description per Debian policy

